body:
✏️Commissions🖌

I’m nearly finished with exams which means I’ll be able to do a couple commissions

I won’t be able to use my iPad (what I usually use ) so I experimenting with firealpaca and other laptop softwares

If you’re interested dm me , I have a few to complete still but will be hoping to finish 1 commission per week xx

Half way through the summer I’m going to put a small price of £3 on each commission (+ £1 per additional character ) so that I can get a little money for my traditional artwork and clothing designs x💓🌻

summary: I had so much fun drawing ruff versions of Umi and Fuu to go along with Hikaru.  I recently started drawing and painting at the...
caption:
I had so much fun drawing ruff versions of Umi and Fuu to go along with Hikaru.

I recently started drawing and painting at the same time and it’s been such a fun way to design a drawing. I feel like I still haven’t fully figured out a process, as it can be a bit messy, especially when it comes to cleaning up the drawing later. But while I’m doing it and while I’m not thinking of the next step, it’s super fluid and relaxing.
